## Empty state

If the customer has no NFC items assigned:
- Centered illustration area — a large muted `CreditCard` icon (80px, `text-gray-300`)
- "No cards yet" heading
- "Your NFC cards will appear here once they've been set up by Beem Hive" subtext in muted text
- No action button — customer cannot self-assign cards

