## What NOT to do

- Do not make per-card Supabase requests for tap counts — fetch counts in the initial query
- Do not compute "taps today" with a separate Supabase query — derive it client-side from the already-fetched tap data
- Do not show a full-page spinner — use skeleton cards
- Do not open the profile URL in the same tab — always `target="_blank"` with `rel="noopener noreferrer"`
- Do not install a clipboard library — use `navigator.clipboard.writeText()` with an `execCommand` fallback
- Do not use `<form>` tags
- Do not show raw Supabase error messages to the user